00:18:31,330 --> 00:18:33,490
Princess. 
 Young Master.

262
00:18:37,900 --> 00:18:42,100
Princess. Don't blame Shiqing's father for being too cruel.

263
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:46,070
There's an old saying that an uncut gem is not useful.

264
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:48,870
Everything is for the good of Third Young Master.

265
00:18:48,870 --> 00:18:50,970
Shiqing lost his mother at a young age.

266
00:18:50,970 --> 00:18:55,600
How could Shiqing's father not educate him?

267
00:18:55,600 --> 00:18:59,030
However, Shiqing has finally lived up to his father's expectations.

268
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:01,940
Didn't you marry him?

269
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:03,950
Won't you eat a little more?

270
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:06,480
The dishes are getting cold. Here.

271
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,990
There's nothing to be afraid of if the dishes get cold.

272
00:19:07,990 --> 00:19:10,790
The scariest thing is a cold heart.

273
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:17,020
To think that in the end, an outsider came to help me.

274
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:30,060
Look at his attitude. I doubt he can still hold on much more.

275
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:32,140
How long can the Princess protect you?

276
00:19:32,140 --> 00:19:36,150
A dignified princess married a blind man!

277
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:44,900
Just then, didn't I really have the stance of the Princess?

278
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:48,340
- Acting as the Princess isn't that hard. 
- Shh!

279
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:52,190
- Lower your voice. 
- I got it, there are ears listening everywhere.

280
00:19:55,990 --> 00:20:00,420
Xiao Wanzi, you must remember to keep a low profile.

281
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:02,630
Don't interfere with what you shouldn't interfere with

282
00:20:02,630 --> 00:20:04,910
and don't say what you shouldn't say.

283
00:20:04,910 --> 00:20:09,070
After wandering Jianghu for so many years, I understand that principle at least.

284
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:13,460
Earlier, it was only because I seriously couldn't watch any longer and helped impulsively.

285
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:17,710
But, I promise that I'll try to keep a low profile in the future.

286
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:21,530
Alright, I'll trust you once more.

287
00:20:21,530 --> 00:20:24,870
Next time, don't act rashly and speak impulsively again!

288
00:20:24,870 --> 00:20:26,900
Our lives are in your hands.

289
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:28,300
We all depend on you, got it?

290
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:32,050
Okay, okay. You're so young to be blabbering like an old lady.

291
00:20:32,050 --> 00:20:34,230
You're the one who's an old lady!

292
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:49,710
Princess, the Young Master is hurt quite badly.

293
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:53,540
Why did you have to speak against General Mei?

294
00:20:53,540 --> 00:20:56,940
He's the master of the family, can't you give him some face?

295
00:20:56,940 --> 00:20:57,920
Shut up.

296
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:00,060
Is this how you speak to your savior?

297
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:04,560
At least I saved you! If I hadn't, who knows how badly you would've been whipped.

298
00:21:04,560 --> 00:21:06,730
- Who asked for your help?
- I--

299
00:21:06,730 --> 00:21:11,270
the Princess actually cares about the Prince Consort.

300
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:14,360
However, she hopes that he can care more about himself.

301
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:16,190
Right, Princess?

302
00:21:22,410 --> 00:21:24,280
Siheng,

303
00:21:25,100 --> 00:21:27,350
I'll dress the Young Master's wound.

304
00:21:37,380 --> 00:21:39,620
You're hurt so badly.

305
00:21:39,620 --> 00:21:42,680
If it hurts, yell it out and don't hold it in, okay?

306
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:46,110
Seriously, General Mei. He had to go so hard.

307
00:21:46,110 --> 00:21:47,680
Is this even his own son?

308
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:50,970
-Someone might thing he holds a large grudge against you.
-Shut up.

309
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,950
Are you exacting vengeance on me?

310
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:02,710
What did you say?

311
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:07,450
Don't interfere with my life.

312
00:22:07,450 --> 00:22:09,390
As if I want to!

313
00:22:09,390 --> 00:22:10,920
It's all because-!

314
00:22:11,980 --> 00:22:15,250
It's fine if you don't say thanks, what's with this atittude?

315
00:22:15,250 --> 00:22:20,080
Fine, I was being nosy, alright? I was being nosy!

316
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:22,840
Since you say that,

317
00:22:22,840 --> 00:22:24,240
then,

318
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:27,850
I still have to say something.

319
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,590
Quit bothering!

320
00:22:34,460 --> 00:22:36,650
- I--
- We're all one family.

321
00:22:36,650 --> 00:22:40,820
As long as you both have common interests, you can live harmoniously.

322
00:22:40,820 --> 00:22:43,170
Won't that be okay?

323
00:22:43,170 --> 00:22:45,390
She's right, she's right! Princess,

324
00:22:45,390 --> 00:22:47,690
We've all noticed your care for the Young Master.

325
00:22:47,690 --> 00:22:50,550
We all...respect that.

326
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:51,950
Respect!

327
00:22:52,740 --> 00:22:54,870
It's just breaking up from your family, what's so hard about that?

328
00:22:54,870 --> 00:22:56,740
Build a wall in the yard

329
00:22:56,740 --> 00:22:59,640
and you'll be so peaceful with your own space.

330
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:01,590
If it's that easy,

331
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:03,390
then you go do it.

332
00:23:04,610 --> 00:23:09,420
Do you think making a weak lady build a wall is reasonable?

333
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:11,230
Are you weak?

334
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,860
I can go build it.

335
00:23:15,860 --> 00:23:19,210
But, the problem is, if I do successfully build it, what happens?

336
00:23:19,210 --> 00:23:21,060
What do you mean?

337
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:24,270
If you want money, say it.

338
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:26,510
Qiao Yun and Siheng will bear witness.

339
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:29,930
If I, the Princess, build this wall,

340
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:31,460
then you, Mei Sanshao,

341
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:35,060
will have to respectfully and earnestly

342
00:23:35,060 --> 00:23:37,980
bow down to me and thank me.

343
00:23:37,980 --> 00:23:39,760
Good luck.

344
00:23:43,390 --> 00:23:45,210
Princess!

345
00:23:45,210 --> 00:23:46,830
Goodness.

346
00:23:50,150 --> 00:23:52,780
- Princess, where are you going?
- Princess,

347
00:23:52,780 --> 00:23:54,580
Don't be angry, Young Master isn't picking on you!

348
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:57,860
Don't just see that he is young and accomplished, talented, handsome and charismatic!

349
00:23:57,860 --> 00:24:01,000
Actually, he lost his mother at a young age

350
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:02,610
and his father is like that.

351
00:24:02,610 --> 00:24:05,110
He's very sensitive, he needs to be protected.

352
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:07,610
He's also really afraid of spiders.

353
00:24:07,610 --> 00:24:10,470
A grown man who's afraid of spiders?

354
00:24:10,470 --> 00:24:12,290
That's funny.

355
00:24:12,290 --> 00:24:15,010
Our Young Master isn't afraid of pain or death,

356
00:24:15,010 --> 00:24:16,930
but he's really afraid of spiders.

357
00:24:16,930 --> 00:24:18,510
I ask you to keep that in mind, please.

358
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:20,460
Enough, enough, I got it so stop talking.

359
00:24:20,460 --> 00:24:21,990
Take me to the Housekeeper

360
00:24:21,990 --> 00:24:24,560
to ask for men and materials. We'll build the wall right now.

361
00:24:24,560 --> 00:24:26,640
No matter what you say, I will make him

362
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,820
-thank me in person!
-Yes!

363
00:24:28,820 --> 00:24:30,100
Also, take that side down.

364
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:32,110
Housekeeper Tao.

365
00:24:32,110 --> 00:24:33,300
What is your command, Princess?

366
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:35,630
Call for more guards and get men.

367
00:24:35,630 --> 00:24:37,060
We're building a wall.

368
00:24:37,060 --> 00:24:38,880
Building a wall?

369
00:24:39,760 --> 00:24:41,300
What wall?

370
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:45,210
Just, a wall. What other kind of wall is there?

371
00:24:45,210 --> 00:24:48,830
Princess, to build a wall, we must prepare the materials.

372
00:24:48,830 --> 00:24:50,570
The hour is getting late.

373
00:24:50,570 --> 00:24:53,490
How about tomorrow? How about if I send people over tomorrow?

374
00:24:53,490 --> 00:24:55,290
Tomorrow, then.

375
00:24:55,290 --> 00:24:58,050
Remember to get lots of people early tomorrow morning, okay?

376
00:24:58,050 --> 00:24:59,520
Yes.

377
00:25:02,790 --> 00:25:05,400
Madam, I have something to report to you.

378
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,620
Go ahead.

379
00:25:06,620 --> 00:25:08,880
Princess came to me in a rush.

380
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,490
She asked for men and materials to build a wall.

381
00:25:10,490 --> 00:25:13,910
I didn't know whether I should agree or not, so I pushed it back to tomorrow.

382
00:25:13,910 --> 00:25:15,090
- Build a wall? 
- Build a wall?

383
00:25:15,090 --> 00:25:16,810
What wall?

384
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:21,510
If my guess is right, it probably to seal the wall of the third courtyard.

385
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:23,290
Has that Mei Shiqing lost his mind?

386
00:25:23,290 --> 00:25:26,860
I'll go tell my father right now so that even the Princess can't save him.

387
00:25:26,860 --> 00:25:29,200
