391
00:25:39,050 --> 00:25:41,010
Mother, you're right.

392
00:25:41,010 --> 00:25:43,570
- Tao Juzheng. 
- Yes.

393
00:25:43,570 --> 00:25:46,200
If Third Young Master needs anything,

394
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:48,180
then try to help him.

395
00:25:48,180 --> 00:25:51,770
You must cooperate with me.

396
00:25:52,490 --> 00:25:54,910
Yes, I understand.

397
00:25:57,910 --> 00:25:59,080
Mother.

398
00:25:59,080 --> 00:26:02,010
Shiyuan, when you come across problems, you have to get it together.

399
00:26:02,010 --> 00:26:04,340
Don't always act like a child.

400
00:26:04,340 --> 00:26:07,880
I got it, mother. What you say is right.

401
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:12,620
Let's sit and wait for the show tomorrow.

402
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:19,200
I've been here for so many days...

403
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:22,100
There's someone guarding outside everyday.

404
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:24,800
How do I get out?

405
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,800
Master Bao? You-

406
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:33,200
Who are you guys? Why are you in my home?

407
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:35,000
We're your subordinates!

408
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:37,700
-Go! Go!
-Let's go. Let's go.

409
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,600
Why are you here?

410
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:47,500
Why am I here?

411
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,700
I'm coming back to my room.

412
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:55,000
Why are you here? You came to find me?

413
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,800
N-No. Hey, hey!

414
00:26:56,800 --> 00:27:00,200
I can't get out anyways, so where would I be if not here?

415
00:27:04,700 --> 00:27:06,500
-Hey!
-You-

416
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:10,400
As of now, you can't accept

417
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,800
our feelings...

418
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:17,800
We...have feelings?

419
00:27:17,800 --> 00:27:19,200
Alright...

420
00:27:20,100 --> 00:27:22,200
It's fine if we don't.

421
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:27,200
I, Master Bao, don't force women.

422
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,900
Let me tell you.

423
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:32,800
Actually, I think you're the best man among the bandits!

424
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:35,600
I think you're responsible and courageous,

425
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:39,600
and you're also handsome! I really really admire you!

426
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:41,800
You really admire me?

427
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,000
Really admire you!

428
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:46,200
Look! I don't talk to anyone else. I only talk to you.

429
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,000
Then in the future,

430
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:52,400
I'll come talk to you everyday.

431
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,000
There's no need for that...

432
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:58,200
Then look here...Big Brother Master Bao...

433
00:27:58,200 --> 00:28:01,800
If you like me so much, then can you promise me something?

434
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:03,400
Speak!

435
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:08,200
Can you let me go? Just treat it as doing a good deed.

436
00:28:08,200 --> 00:28:11,200
Once I get out, I'll grab a bunch of money and come repay you!

437
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:13,800
I-I'll really come repay you. Alright?

438
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:14,800
Alright!

439
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:16,700
Really?

440
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:20,800
Are you trying to-

441
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:31,200
What are you doing?

442
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:37,600
D-Didn't you say you wouldn't force me?

443
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:40,000
Force you?

444
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:42,200
What are you going to do?

445
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:45,200
I know...

446
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:51,200
I know you aren't asleep!

447
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:53,600
S-Stop pretending.

448
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:04,000
He's really asleep?

449
00:29:06,000 --> 00:29:09,200
He had the guards leave earlier...

450
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:12,400
Today's my chance to escape!

451
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:28,400
Young Master Bao!

452
00:29:30,600 --> 00:29:32,200
Why is Master Bao shorter today?

453
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:34,300
That's right. What's going on?

454
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:37,000
Stop running!

455
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,800
Young Master Bao!

456
00:29:42,400 --> 00:29:45,000
If you don't want to die, then stay here quietly.

457
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:46,700
Hurry up!

458
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:52,400
Young Master Bao!

459
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:54,800
Someone ran away wearing your clothes!

460
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:57,600
Are you crazy? Are you still dreaming in the middle of the night?

461
00:29:57,600 --> 00:29:59,800
Really! There really was someone!

462
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:01,600
Also! Ask him! Ask him!

463
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:04,000
That's right! I also saw it!

464
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:06,000
Someone's running over there!

465
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:08,000
Hurry, hurry, hurry! Go chase them! Hurry up!

466
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:10,100
Ok, ok, ok!

467
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:23,200
If it wasn't because of me, you would've died there! Do you know that?

468
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:26,000
Thank you then.

469
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:32,770
Do you know what sort of people are in Green Dragon Fort?

470
00:30:32,770 --> 00:30:34,500
They're a bunch of bandits!

471
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:38,200
If you were caught by them, do you know what would happen?

472
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:41,100
Aren't you a bandit? Aren't you?

473
00:30:44,100 --> 00:30:46,000
The Green Dragon Fort is full of traps.

474
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:48,600
You can't escape. Stop trying to.

475
00:30:50,540 --> 00:30:52,400
Take off your clothes.

476
00:30:55,300 --> 00:30:57,800
What are you looking at? Those are my clothes!

477
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:59,100
Take them off!

478
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:03,000
I'll take them off then. What are you yelling for?

479
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:09,200
I won't take advantage of you.

480
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:13,000
I'll wait for you outside. Leave the clothes on the ground after you take them off.

481
00:31:14,800 --> 00:31:16,700
I won't take them off!

482
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:30,400
Let's work hard everyone!

483
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:31,800
After construction's complete today,

484
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:35,200
I'll treat everyone to a banquet of wine and meat!

485
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,200
-How's that?
-Ok!

486
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,800
Thank you, Princess!

487
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:43,000
Who would've thought the Princess understands so much?

488
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:50,400
My Lord, I heard the kapok flowers are just in bloom across the yard.

489
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,800
Let's go take a look.

490
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:55,200
I am never interested in these things.

491
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:59,200
Father, kapok trees are also called "hero trees", and their flowers are called "hero flowers".

492
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:04,000
Only such handsome and elegant plants are worthy of a hero such as Father's appreciation.

493
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:05,600
Keep talking.

494
00:32:05,600 --> 00:32:07,000
It's said that Nan Jiang Island

495
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:11,400
once had a hero who died fighting against other clans.

496
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:21,700
In the past...there wasn't a wall here.

497
00:32:21,700 --> 00:32:25,600
That's right! What's going on?

498
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:28,800
In response to Madam's question, this seems to be Third Young Master's yard.

499
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:32,000
This wall...should have been just built.

500
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:35,000
T-This Third Young Master's actions are too severe!

501
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,300
He's built a wall within the house!

502
00:32:37,300 --> 00:32:38,800
My Lord!

503
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:42,600
He's not respecting you at all!

504
00:32:42,600 --> 00:32:44,600
That's right, Father.

505
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,200
Bring me a ladder!

506
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:49,600
Hurry!

507
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:52,400
You're not doing it right. Come down and I'll do it.

508
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:55,300
Please be careful then, Princess.

509
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:57,000
You can climb up.

510
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:05,000
-Father.
-Princess?

511
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,600
Why aren't you going through the entrance?

512
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:09,400
I would like to go through the entrance.

513
00:33:09,400 --> 00:33:12,200
I forgot to make a door...

514
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,600
Mei Shiqing!

515
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:20,200
Who allowed you to build a wall!

516
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:23,130
